skill.name: Training Dummy
skill.desc: Use on a champion to spawn a movable target dummy nearby. Cannot be used in combat.

skill.name: World Ender
skill.desc: Transform for 12 seconds, gaining 15% and converting all bonus Attack Speed to Attack Damage. While transformed, attacks deal physical damage.

skill.name: Essence Theft
skill.desc:
Steal essence from enemies around her target, dealing magic damage and 20% Mana Reaving them.

Every 3 casts, instead, unleash a wave that deals magic damage to all enemies hit. This deals 33% more damage to enemies whose essence has been stolen.

lonia Bonus: +3 Mana per second

skill.name: Comeuppance
skill.desc: Lock on to the farthest enemy and unleash a hail of 6 shots toward them. Each deals physical damage to the first enemy hit.

skill.name: Moonlight Vigil
skill.desc:
Fire a moon blast at the largest group of enemies that deals physical damage to enemies within 2 hexes. Equip 3 Chakram, plus 1 more for each enemy hit by the moon blast.

For 7 seconds, attacks deal bonus physical damage for each Chakram equipped. 50% of damage dealt by Chakrams heals Aphelios.

skill.name: Volley
skill.desc:
Fire 8 arrows in a cone, each dealing physical damage to the first enemy hit and Chilling them for a few seconds.

Chill: Reduced Attack Speed by 30%

skill.name: Arise!
skill.desc:
Passive: After every third attack from Azir, a Sand Soldier deals 105 magic damage to their target.

Active: Summon a Sand Soldier to attack your target. It Azir already has 3 Soldiers, they all immediately deal magic damage instead.
stats: Max Soldier Strike: 85% of Soldier Damage

skill.name: Corrosive Acid
skill.desc:
Passive: Cast every 2 attacks and cycle between 3 different Abilities.
Active: Lob there pools of acid towards the largest group of enemies, dealing magic damage and 60% Shredding and Sundering enemies for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Royal Malestrom
skill.desc: Lash out at the lowest Health enemy in range 6 times. Each lash deals physical damage and 2% of the target's max Health as true damage.
stats: Number of Lashes: 6 + 5 per 100% bonus AS

skill.name: Twin Fang
skill.desc:
Deal magic damage to the current target and Wound them for 5 seconds. If they are already Wounded, deal bonus magic damage.

Wound: Reduce healing received by 33%

skill.name: Feast
skill.desc: Deal magic damage to the lowest adjacent Health enemy. If this kills them, devour them and permanetly gain max Health.

skill.name: Noxian Guillotine
skill.desc: Deal physical damage to the current target. If they die, immediately cast this again with damage.

skill.name: Phase Dive
skill.desc: Heal 20% of damage taken in the last 4 seconds and deal magic damage to the current target.

skill.name: Shield of Durand
skill.desc: Reduce damage taken and heal for over 4 seconds. After, deal magic damage to adjacent enemies.

skill.name: Judgement
skill.desc: Spin times every second for the next 4 seconds. Each spin deals physical damage to adjacent enemies.
stats: Number of Spins: 2 + 1 per 50% bonus AS

skill.name: Snip Snip!
skill.desc:
Dash around the current target and snip 3 times in a cone, each dealing magic damage to enemies hit.

Every 3 casts, Armor and Magic resist for 2 seconds.

skill.name: CH-3X Lightning Grenade
skill.desc:
Hurl a grenade towards the largest group of enemies, dealing magic damage to enemies in a large area and Stunning them for 1.5 seconds.

4 Star Upgrade: YES YES YES, IT WORKS!!!

skill.name: H-28G Laser Beam
skill.desc: Heimerdinger's turret fires a laser beam in its target's direction, dealing to all enemies it passes through.

skill.name: Defiant Dance
skill.desc:
Enter a defensive stance and gain Shield that rapidly decays over 3 seconds. When it breaks, deal magic damage + 30% of the damage absorbed to enemies around and in front of Irelia.

Ionia Bonus: +25 Armor and Magic Resist

skill.name: Cataclysm
skill.desc: Mightily leap on a nearby enemy. Deal magic damage to enemies within 2 hexes and Stun them.

skill.name: Acceleration Blast
skill.desc: Grant Attack Speed to Jayce and adjacent allies on his left and right for 3 seconds. Fire a blast at the current target, which explodes on the first enemy hit, dealing physical damage to enemies near the blast.

skill.name: Curtain Call
skill.desc:
Take aim at the current target and deal physical damage to enemies in a line; each hit reduces damage by 40%.

Ionia Bonus: +20% Attack Damage

skill.name: Fishbones!
skill.desc: Fire 5 rockets at random enemies within 2 hexes of the current target. Each rocket deals physical damage.

skill.name: Icathian Rain
skill.desc: Dash away from all enemies, then fire missiles split across the 4 nearest enemies. Each missile deal magic damage.

skill.name: Pierce and Rend
skill.desc:
Passive : Attacks impale a spear in the target, which deals true damage when removed. Kalista rips the spears out if it would kill the target.

Active: Impale 6 spears in the current target.

skill.name: Inner Flame
skill.desc:
Fire a burst of energy at Karma's target that explodes upon impact, dealing magic damage to adjacent enemies. Every third cast launches 3 bursts of energy.

Ionia Bonus: +20% Ability Power

skill.name: Force Pulse
skill.desc:
Gain Shield for 4 seconds. Deal magic damage to enemies in a cone and Disarm them for a while.

Disarm: Cannot move or attack, but CAN cast spells

skill.name: Voracity
skill.desc:
Throw three daggers that land next to enemies within two hexes. Then, teleport to each to deal magic damage to adjacent enemies and Wound them for 6 seconds.

Wound: Reduce healing received by 50%

skill.name: Divine Ascent
skill.desc:
Passive: Kayle gains new Passive effects as your Tactician levels up.
Level 1: Attacks deal bonus magic damage.
Level 6: Every 3rd attack launches a wave that deals magic damage and Shreds enemies for 3 seconds.
Level 9: Every attack launches a wave and they travel farther.

skill.name: Skaaaaaaarl!
skill.desc:
Passive: Start combat with Shield. When it breaks, dismount and gain stacking Attack Speed for the rest of combat.

Active: Remount and gain Shield.

4 Star Upgrade: Execute enemies under 25% Health.

skill.name: All Out Strike
skill.desc:
Heal for max Health. Knock up the current target before smashing them to the edge of the battlefield. Deal magic damage and Stun them for few seconds. Deal magic damage to enemies the target collides with and Stun them for few second.

If the target can't be pushed back any further, knock them off the battlefield. Otherwise, K'Sante will chase after them.

skill.name: Frozen Tomb
skill.desc: Stun the current target for 2 seconds and deal magic damage to enemies within 2 hexes of them. They take 10% more damage for the next 4 seconds.

skill.name: Torrent of Light
skill.desc: Channel a barrage of light at the current target that deals magic damage over a few seconds, reducing their Magic Resistance every seconds. If they die, shift to a new target.

skill.name: Call of the Void
skill.desc: Open two portals near the current target. Destroy 50% of shields and deal magic damage to all enemies caught between the portals.

skill.name: Sap Magic
skill.desc:
Passive: Whenever an enemy uses their ability, gain 5 Mana.

Active: On Maokai's next attack, heal.

skill.name: Soul Eater
skill.desc:
Steal max Health, 10% Attack Damage, and Defenses from the nearest enemies for 8 seconds.

While empowered, every third attack deals physical damage.

skill.name: Command: Protect
skill.desc: Grant the lowest Health ally Shield for 4 seconds and empowers Orianna's next attack to deal bonus magic damage.

skill.name: Steadfast Hammer
skill.desc:
Gain Shield for 3 seconds. Deal magic damage to the current target.

4 Star Upgrade: Knock the target into the largest clump of enemies, dealing 33% of the target's max Health as magic damage to the target and 15% of that amount to the clump. Stun them for 0.25 seconds.

skill.name: Furious Bite
skill.desc:
Deal physical damage to the current target. If they are below 70% Health, this damage is converted to true damage.

If this kills the target, rip through them 1 hex and heal Health.

skill.name: Cull the Meek
skill.desc: Deal magic damage to adjacent enemies. Heal for the first enemy hit and another for each additional one.

skill.name: Void Charge
skill.desc: Rift Herald charges at the furthest enemy and crashes into the first enemy hit. The crash deals magic damage and stuns for  seconds all nearby enemies.

skill.name: Realm Warp
skill.desc:
Wanderers' spells change depending on the Region Portal players voted for at the start of the game.

Bandle City
Ryze creates a portal to Bandle City underneath a random unit on your bench. After a brief delay, they arrive on the battlefield with bonus mana and are...slightly smaller?

Demacia
Ryze creates a portal to Demacia underneath a cluster of injured allies, granting Shield for 2 seconds. If an ally leaves the safety of the portal, they are healed for Health. When the portal expires, enemies within are dealt magic damage.

Freljord
Ryze creates a portal to the Freljord underneath a random group of enemies for 3 seconds. The freezing winds deal magic damage to enemies within two hexes over the duration and apply Permafrost, a permanent Chill.
If enemies are already affected by Permafrost, they are instead Stunned for the duration.
Chill: Reduce Attack Speed by 30%

Ionia
Ryze creates a portal to Ionia, summoning forth a Spirit Tree that affects the closest units. Allies are invigorated, gaining Attack Speed for 6 seconds and restoring Health over the duration. Enemies are pacified, causing them to dance.

Noxus
Ryze creates a portal to Noxus' armory that spews out a torrent of weapons and armor, granting completed items to random allies with open slots, and throwing Axes towards random enemies that deal magic damage each.
If any ally would recieve an item while all slots are full, they instead gain a stacking 40% damage increase for the rest of combat.

Piltover
Ryze summons a portal to Piltover that launches out an enforcer grenade towards his target, dealing magic damage to enemies within two hexes and creating a containment area for seconds. Enemies are unable to leave the area, and of the damage dealt to them is also dealt to all other enemies within.

Shadow Isles
Ryze creates a portal to the Shadow Isles, reclaiming lost ally's souls. They return to the battlefield, with % of their maximum Health.
If no allies have died yet, the portal remains open, waiting for an ally to die. Ryze cannot resurrect himself.

Shurima
Ryze creates a portal to Shurima, summoning a gigantic sand tornado that travels across the battlefield, dealing magic damage to enemies hit and knocking them up briefly.
The tornado has chance to unearthed burried treasures and gold as it travels.

Targon
Ryze creates a portal to the skies above Mount Targon that beckons his target. After a few seconds, they descend from the heavens as a meteor towards the largest cluster of enemies, dealing % of the the initial target's maximum Health as magic damage and knocking up enemies in the epicenter.

Zaun
Open portals to Zuan, causing hired guns to fire a torrent of munitions at a nearby enemy that deal magic damage and apply 50% Wound, 40% Shred, and 40% Sunder for 6 seconds. The more gold you have, the more power the portals become.
25 Gold: +1 Portal. Portals fire a rocket that deals 50% damage in a one-hex radius
50 Gold: Double the portals. Summon +2 additional portals for every 15 Gold more.

skill.name: Realm Warp: Bandle City
skill.desc:
Create a portal to Bandle City under a Most expensive Unit on your bench. They are summoned to the battlefield with bonus Mana and are...slightly smaller?

If there are no units left on your bench, Ryze summons a high tier unit from the shop instead.

skill.name: Realm Warp: Demacia
skill.desc:
Create a portal to Demacia that protects allies for 2 seconds. Allies within the zone gain Shield. If an ally leaves the safety of the portal, they are healed for 250.

When the portal expires, enemies within are dealt magic damage.

skill.name: Realm Warp: Freljord
skill.desc:
Create a portal to the Freljord under a random group of enemies for 2 seconds. The freezing winds deal magic damage to enemies within two hexes over the duration and apply Permafrost, a permanent Chill.

If enemies are already affected by Permafrost, they are instead Stunned for the duration
Chill: Reduce Attack Speed by 30%

skill.name: Realm Warp: Ionia
skill.desc: Create a portal to Ionia in the center of the battlefield, summoning forth a Spirit Tree that affects the closest units. Allies gain Attack Speed for 6 seconds and are healed for over the duration. Enemies dance, Stunning them for 2 seconds.

skill.name: Realm Warp: Noxus
skill.desc:
Create a portal to Noxus that spews out a torrent of weapons and armor, granting completed items to random allies with open slots, and throwing axes towards random enemies that deal magic damage each.

If an ally would recieve an item while all slots are full, they instead gain a stacking 10% damage increase for the rest of combat.

skill.name: Realm Warp: Piltover
skill.desc: Ryze summons a portal to Piltover that launches out an enforcer grenade towards his targets largest clump, dealing magic damage to enemies within two hexes and creating a containment area for seconds. Enemies are unable to leave the area, and of the damage dealt to them is also dealt to all other enemies within.

skill.name: Realm Warp: Shadow Isles
skill.desc:
Mark the Lowest Health % ally's soul(s) to be reclaimed by the Shadow Isles. After they die, they return to the battlefield with of their maximum Health.

If all living allies are already marked, Ryze instead resurrects a deceased ally. Ryze cannot resurrect himself.

skill.name: Realm Warp: Shurima
skill.desc:
Create a portal to Shurima, summoning a sand tornado that travels across the battlefield, dealing magic damage to enemies hit and knocking them up, Stunning them for second.

The tornado has a chance to unearth buried treasures and gold as it travels.

skill.name: Realm Warp: Targon
skill.desc:
Create a portal to the skies above Mount Targon that beckons the current target. After a few seconds, they descend from the heavens as a meteor towards the largest group of enemies, dealing of the the initial target's maximum Health as magic damage. Enemies in the epicenter are briefly knocked up.

If the target is the only enemy remaining, they never descend.

skill.name: Realm Warp: Zaun
skill.desc:
Create portals to Zaun, causing hired guns to fire at nearby enemies. Deals magic damage and Wounds, 40% Shreds, and 40% Sunders for 6 seconds. The more gold you have, the more powerful the portals become.

25 Gold: +1 portal. Portals fire a rocket that deals 50% damage in a one-hex radius.
50 Gold: Double the portals. Summon 1 additional portals for every 20 Gold more.

skill.name: Flair
skill.desc: Shoot at the current target and deal to the first enemy hit. Reduce their Armor by 10.

skill.name: Fury of the North
skill.desc:
Passive: Whenever an ally attacks a Chilled enemy, they deal bonus true damage.

Active: Gain Shield for 4 seconds. Deal magic damage to nearby enemies and Chill them for 4 seconds.

Chill: Reduced Attack Speed by 30%

skill.name: Dawning Shadow
skill.desc: Fire a massive beam at the furthest enemy, dealing physical damage to all enemies hit. Any allies hit gain Shield for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Facebreaker
skill.desc:
Pull in an enemy on either side and slam them together, dealing magic damage and Stunning them.

If only one enemy is grabbed, the damage and Stun duration are increased by 50%.

Ionia Bonus: +200 max Health

skill.name: Ki Barrier
skill.desc:
Gain Shield and grant Shield to the 2 lowest Health allies for 4 seconds. After shielding his allies, Shen's shield refreshes with a burst, dealing magic damage to adjacent enemies.

Ionia Bonus: +9% Damage Reduction

skill.name: Glory in Death
skill.desc:
Passive: Upon death, reanimate with 100% Health, decaying at max Health per second. Sion can no longer use his abilityo, but is immune to Crowd Control and gains Attack Speed.

Active: Charge towards the most enemies within 3 hexes. Deal to any enemies along the way and Stun them for 1.5 seconds.

skill.name: Crescendo
skill.desc: Send a wave of sound at the largest clump of enemies and deal magic damage to enemies hit. Allies hit by the wave gain Attack Speed for 5 seconds.

skill.name: Astral Infusion
skill.desc:
Heal the lowest health ally. If the ally is below 50% Health, increase the amount healed by 33%.

The ally is infused for 5 seconds, calling down 5 stars over the duration that deal magic damage to the closest enemy.

skill.name: Demonflare
skill.desc: Transform and gain max Health for 5 seconds. While transformed, deal magic damage to enemies within 2 hexes every second.

skill.name: Seismic Shove
skill.desc:
Passive: Whenever an enemy is knocked up by anything, throw a boulder at them, which deals magic damage.

Active: Knock up the current target for 2 seconds.

skill.name: Radiance
skill.desc: Gain Shield for 6 seconds. It absorbs damage received by adjacent allies.

skill.name: Noxious Trap
skill.desc:
Hurl an explosive mushroom at the current target. When it detonates, enemies within 1 hex are Wounded and take magic damage over 3 seconds.

4 Star Upgrade: Increase the explosion radius by 1 hex.

Wounded: Reduced healing received by 50%

skill.name: Powering Up
skill.desc:
T-Hex is still powering up and has no Ablity. Once she reaches 20 Power, gain hextech Breath.

Hextech Breath: Breathe flames in a cone, dealing magic damage in all enemies hit.

skill.name: Rapid Fire
skill.desc:
Gain 50% Attack Speed for 4 seconds. For the duration, attacks explode on impact and deal physical damage to enemies within 1 hex.

4 Star Upgrade: Every 10th attack deals bonus physical damage and ricochets to the largest clump of enemies, dealing physical damage to enemies within 1 hex.

skill.name: Disdain
skill.desc:
Passive: Whenever an enemy enters attack range, fire a blast from the leg facing that direction, dealing physical damage to them. Each of Urgot's 6 legs has a 4 second cooldown.

Active: Gain Shield for 5 seconds and dash behind the current target. Reset all leg colldowns.

skill.name: Plasma Fission
skill.desc: Fire a plasma bolt towards the current target that deals to the first enemy hit. It then splits in two, dealing 50% less damage whenever it passes through an enemy.

skill.name: Blast Shield
skill.desc:
Gain Shield for 4 seconds. Deal physical damage to enemies within 1 hex of the current target and Sunder them for 4 seconds.

Sunder: Reduced Armor by 40%

skill.name: Blade of the Ruined King
skill.desc: Deal magic damage to the current target. For the rest of combat, Viego's attacks deal bonus stacking magic damage.

skill.name: Void Shield
skill.desc: Void Remora curls into a defensive position for 2 seconds, gaining shield. When the shield expires, it explodes, dealing to all nearby enemies.

skill.name: Primal Howl
skill.desc:
Passive: Warwick's attacks to be converted on-hit magic damage.

Active: For the next 2.5 seconds, the passive healing is increased by 50%. After, Stun adjacent enemies for 1.25 seconds.

skill.name: Last Breath
skill.desc:
Send a whirlwind at the furthest enemy within 3 hexes, Stunning all enemies hit. Dash to and slash the original target, dealing physical damage to them. Slam them into the ground and deal physical damage to enemies within 1 hex.

Ionia Bonus: +15% Omnivamp

skill.name: Living Shadow
skill.desc:
Create a shadow at the furthest enemy within 3 hexes. Zed and his shadow slash adjacent enemies, dealing physical damage.

Ionia Bonus: +15% Crit Chance and Crit Damage

skill.name: Surge
skill.desc:
Passive: Execute enemies below 12% Health. Kills reset the duration of Surge.

Active: For the next 9 seconds, attacks chain lightning to 3 additional enemies, dealing physical damage.
